casebody.data:
Doris C. Chlebowski v. Edmond M. Chlebowski (5809)

Spallone, O’Connell and Norcott, Js.

Submitted on briefs February 5 — decision released February 22, 1988 *803Robert P. Hanahan filed a brief for the appellant (plaintiff). Kevin P. Thornton filed a brief for the appellee (defendant). Per Curiam.

The plaintiff’s claims of error implicate the factfinding function and the discretionary powers of the trial court. Our review of the record and transcripts clearly indicate that the court acted properly and in accordance with applicable law.

There is no error.
